"SPELL POOL"

Mages and Shamans use the spell pool to augment any sorcery actions
they make, this includes the actual casting of the spell and any drain
they may take from it. It is equal to their Intelligence + Willpower +
Magic divided by 3.

^WSee Also: SORCERY, MAGES, SHAMANS, POOLS, DRAIN, SDEFENSE, REFLECT^n
